description: Syntax extension system and better error reporting should be finished.  For patterns should be introduced after a few tests by practical usage.

Performance issues should be solved totally. MLStyle.jl must be much faster than Match.jl in all situations.

Some real world applications by MLStyle should be released, like parser generator framework and compiler services.

#101: GlobalRef in patterns.
#99: slurp Tuples
